<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id063e4c2c-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3910"><num value="3910">§ 3910.</num><heading> Kimberley Process Implementation Coordinating Committee</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The President shall establish a Kimberley Process Implementation Coordinating Committee to coordinate the implementation of this chapter. The Committee shall be composed of the following individuals or their designees:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id063e4c2d-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3910/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The Secretary of the Treasury and the Secretary of State, who shall be co-chairpersons.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id063e4c2e-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3910/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The Secretary of Commerce.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id063e4c2f-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3910/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> The United States Trade Representative.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id063e4c30-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3910/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> The Secretary of Homeland Security.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id063e4c31-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3910/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> A representative of any other agency the President deems appropriate.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id063e4c32-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/pl/108/19/s11">Pub. L. 108–19, § 11</ref>, <date date="2003-04-25">Apr. 25, 2003</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/117/635">117 Stat. 635</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
